        { "type": "question", "settings": { "question": "How long does one stick last?", "answer": "Several months with daily use. The concentrated essential oils retain potency for a long time. At $0.03 per use, it's one of the most cost-effective natural remedies available." } },
        { "type": "question", "settings": { "question": "How fast does it work?", "answer": "Seconds. You'll feel the effect immediately upon inhaling. The essential oils reach your nasal passages instantly. The rollerball provides relief within 60 seconds when applied to temples." } },
